info.description: Classic Margherita but with Dragon's Hot & Spicy Fire-Hot Garlic Sauce and Mozzarella on your slice for that extra kick!

info.name: Pesto Margherita Pizza Slice
info.description: Refreshingly Fresh Pesto Sauce and Deliciously Creamy Mozzarella on your Standout Slice!

info.name: Classic Margherita Pizza Slice
info.description: The slice of our heart, now yours! Classic Cheesy Margherita for your soul

info.name: Torpedo Tandoori Chicken Pizza Slice
info.description: Bite into your slice topped with Chicken Tikka, Cherry Tomatoes, Baby Corn, Jalapenos, Olives, Onions, Green Capsicum, & Mozzarella Cheese - Flavour bomb exploded right there!

info.name: Pollo Feta-roni Freak Pizza Slice
info.description: Be as freaky as a slice topped with Spicy Chicken Pepperoni, Tangy Jalapenos, Fabulous Feta Cheese and a Blanket of wholesome Mozzarella.

info.name: Pesto Green Gnome Feta Pizza Slice
info.description: Pesto Paradiso on your Fabulous Feta-licious Slice of Joy with Creamy Feta, Crunchy Baby Corn, Caramelized Onion, Exotic Cherry Tomatoes, Jalapenos, and Mozzarella Cheese

info.name: Vampire Slayer Pizza Slice
info.description: Sshhhhh! Vampire's favourite Veggie Fantasy - Sliced Button Mushrooms, Exotic Cherry Tomatoes, Roasted Garlic Granules served on a Cheesy Personal Slice

info.name: Arabian Nights Pizza Slice
info.description: A slice of whimsy yet standout - Golden Falafels, Roasted Veggies and Mozzarella Cheese!

info.name: Bad Boy Butter Chicken Pizza Slice
info.description: Breaking all the rules and ruling this slice of life! Chicken Tikka, Butter Chicken Gravy, Roasted Veggies and lots of Mozzarella Cheese on your solo slice.

info.name: Dragonfire Paneer Pizza Slice
info.description: A Fiery Slice topped with Schezwan Paneer, Hot Garlic Sauce, Mozzarella Cheese, Onion and Capsicum for the Standout You!

info.name: Verdant Veggie Mosaic Pizza Slice
info.description: A slice of art with Sliced Button Mushrooms, Caramelized Onion, Exotic Cherry Tomatoes, Olives, Capsicum, and loads of Mozzarella - A Standout sight for your tastebuds

info.name: Wild Veggie Paneer Inferno Pizza Slice
info.description: You might wanna just go wild with your Veggie Fantasies because Paneer Tikka, Crunchy Baby Corn, Exotic Cherry Tomatoes, Olives, Jalapenos, Capsicum, Onion, & Mozzarella Cheese on your Slice is here to seize the day, my friend!

info.name: Corn & Pepper Lasagne
info.description: Treat yourself with American flavors in a lasagna with sweetcorn, olives, jalapenos and melted mozzarella on a layer of a pizza sauce and cheese spread.

info.name: Dilli ke Chole Lasagne
info.description: Classic lasagna filled with chatpate chole and layers of chipotle liquid cheese will make your taste buds do the Patiala tango.

info.name: Mughlai Masti Mac N Cheese Pasta (Newly Launched)
info.description: Do away with the conflict between Mughlai or Italian with our Veg Mughlai Mac and Cheese. With Mughlai gravy, topped with creamy mac and cheese will be a Jashn E Bahaar on your taste buds.

info.name: Paneer Tikka Mac N Cheese Pasta
info.description: Find the perfect blend of flavours in our Mac n Cheese which is endowed with sumptuous amount of cheese blended perfectly with the desi flavour of Paneer Tikka.

info.name: Chicken Kheema Lasagne
info.description: ( Safely Cooked Chicken) Our signature Italian dish fused with desi flavors - delicious lasagna layered with Kheema and oozing with cheese. Desi taste, Italian ways.

info.name: Kheema & Sausage Mac N Cheese Pasta
info.description: ( Safely Cooked Chicken) An absolute chicken delight is our loaded Mac N Cheese with flavours of American sausages from the west and spicy kheema from India. These two come together with a creamy mac n cheese to make it a heavenly dish.

info.name: Meatburst Mac N Cheese Pasta
info.description: ( Safely Cooked Chicken) Juicy meatballs with a soft meaty centre on a layer of creamy Mac n Cheese oozing with chipotle and our secret spice mix.

info.name: Punjabi Butter Chicken Mac N Cheese Pasta
info.description: (100% Safely Cooked Chicken) Macaroni pasta laden with cheese sauce and topped with mozzarella cheese with delicious butter chicken filling, a fusion that is unmatched.

info.name: Mexican Toastie
info.description: Crunch into the cheesiness and go full in on this flavourful Mexican Adventure.

info.name: Chilli Cheese Toastie
info.description: Spice things up with the mighty, cheesy it up with the crunchy

info.name: Potato Chilli Shots with Mayo Dip
info.description: Crispy and spiced potato shots served with a cheesy mayonnaise dip to tantalize your tastebuds.

info.name: Chicken Kheema n Cheesy Garlic Bread
info.description: Delicious flatbread packed with spicy, mouth-watering chicken kheema, coated with garlic butter.

info.name: Paneer Calzone
info.description: Folded half-pizza filled with tender, creamy pieces of paneer along with crunchy onions and capscicum makes this a perfect anytime snack to munch on

info.name: Paneer N Cheesy Garlic Bread
info.description: Delicious flatbread baked with garlic butter, topped with copious amounts of paneer and a whole lot of cheese! Take a bite of the perfect side to your standout meal.

info.name: Cheesy Garlic Bread
info.description: Fresh flatbread baked with garlic butter and chefs secret seasoning, infused with creamy el-classico cheese.

info.name: Corn & jalapeno Cheesy Garlic Bread
info.description: Fresh flatbread stuffed with sweet golden American corn & spicy jalapenos, glazed with garlic butter and chefs secret seasoning.

info.name: Plain Herbed Garlic Bread
info.description: Light, super soft bread deliciously glazed with butter, garlic and herbs. Your standout meal is incomplete without this!

info.name: Creamy Dip
info.description: A Creamy molten cheesy dip to suit all your moods. Have it with a Garlic bread or just dip your finger in and relish it just like that!

info.name: Vanilla Ice Cream
info.description: Luxuriously smooth and creamy that melts effortlessly on the tongue, this vanilla ice cream is sure to give you the chills with it's deliciousness. Serving Size - 100ml

info.name: Strawberry Ice Cream
info.description: Nothing tops a berry berry good ice cream and this Strawberry one is pure heaven! Dig into this fruity, creamy Strawberry ice-cream with real Strawberry chunks. Serving Size - 100ml

info.name: Salted Caramel Ice Cream
info.description: Sweet, Salty and a little scoop of happiness. This salted caramel ice cream is sure to melt your heart. Serving Size - 100ml

info.name: Dry Fruit Kulfi Ice Cream
info.description: A creamy base, made from simmering milk to a thick, luscious consistency, with crunchy dry fruits makes for a perfect dessert for your cravings. Serving Size - 100ml

info.name: Alphonso Mango Ice Cream
info.description: Delicious Alphonso Mango based ice cream made with juicy, real Mango pulp and Mango chunks. This is pure heaven for all Mango lovers. Serving Size - 100ml

info.name: Belgian Chocolate Ice Cream
info.description: Treat yourself to a scoop of luxury: Belgian chocolate ice cream that's rich, creamy, and simply irresistible. Serving Size - 100ml

info.name: Choco Lava Cake
info.description: A perfect match of Chocolate Cake on the outside and molten Chocolate on the inside, our Choco Lava cake is every dessert lovers dream come true.

info.description: 475 ML Coca - Cola Bottle

info.name: Biscoff Cheesecake Slice
info.description: A Dreamy, Creamy & Caramelly affair! That's everything you get with every bite of this Delicious Biscoff Slice.

info.name: Triple Chocolate Mousse Jar
info.description: Dig into this chocolatey delight! 3 layers of complete deliciousness made of dark, milk and white chocolate.

info.name: Red Velvet Dessert Jar
info.description: Fluffy red velvet sponge cakes with perfectly sweet cream cheese frosting, layered in a mason jar. This dessert jar is worth the indulgence!

info.name: Chocolate Indulgence Brownie
info.description: Indulge in richly decadent Indulgence brownie crafted with love & topped with bittersweet chocolate that provides ultra-rich chocolate experience.

info.name: Red Velvet Muffin
info.description: Our Red Velvet muffin made with soft sponge filled with delicious cream cheese is sure to give a velvety touch to your tastebuds.

info.name: Chocolate Truffle Pastry
info.description: Layers of soft chocolate sponge and dense but silky-smooth chocolate ganache makes this cake a decadent celebration.

info.name: Rich Red Velvet Pastry
info.description: Rich and moist Red Velvet cake layered with fresh cream cheese makes our Red Velvet pastry difficult to share. Youll think twice too.
